<!DOCTYPE lake>
<html>
 <head>
  <meta name="\&quot;doc-version\&quot;" content="\&quot;1\&quot;" />
  <meta name="\&quot;viewport\&quot;" content="\&quot;adapt\&quot;" />
  <meta name="\&quot;typography\&quot;" content="\&quot;classic\&quot;" />
  <meta name="\&quot;paragraphSpacing\&quot;" content="\&quot;relax\&quot;" />
  <meta name="\&quot;defaultFontsize\&quot;" content="\&quot;16\&quot;" />
 </head>
 <body>
  <h2 data-lake-id="\&quot;8e1b944f\&quot;" id="\&quot;8e1b944f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua1cfc727\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua1cfc727\&quot;">背景</span></h2>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u26fc397c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u26fc397c\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u13d0df96\&quot;" id="\&quot;u13d0df96\&quot;">LLM 写代码很快，但一旦面对长远规划或复杂上下文，就容易“幻觉、降智、迷失方向”</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1d70812a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1d70812a\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf1335e5c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf1335e5c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucd7fdf3a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucd7fdf3a\&quot;">修 bug 一直是个头疼的问题，没有需求这么体系化，却又需要耗费大量人力资源进行处理。为了构建一个自动化的 Bug 修复 Agent，对于代码生成和修复，我们不能仅仅依赖大语言模型（LLM）的自由发散，而是必须将其嵌入到具有强规则、确定性校验、沙箱执行和严格状态机流转的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uda3232d7\&quot;" id="\&quot;uda3232d7\&quot;">硬性工作流</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u86f7962b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u86f7962b\&quot;">中，从而收敛 LLM 的幻觉，保证修复的可靠性。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u19ea1014\&quot;" id="\&quot;u19ea1014\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u24c226e6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u24c226e6\&quot;">Compound AI Systems：</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc31937a7\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc31937a7\&quot;">当前 Agent 发展的核心理论范式</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue8f4524c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue8f4524c\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u6999433d\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u4077e457\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7339a804\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7339a804\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub7c4d0d3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub7c4d0d3\&quot;">核心理念：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufaebfda4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufaebfda4\&quot;"> 解决复杂工程问题，不能靠“一个巨大的模型 + 一段巨大的 Prompt（Omni-Bot 模式）”，而是要构建一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uedc07341\&quot;" id="\&quot;uedc07341\&quot;">复合系统</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufd37bb0f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufd37bb0f\&quot;">。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u4077e457\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;udf3943e5\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf3943e5\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u44568166\&quot;" id="\&quot;u44568166\&quot;">系统组件：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaf9b9b21\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaf9b9b21\&quot;"> 这个系统应该包含：模型（LLMs）、外部工具（编译器、Linter、搜索）、检索器（RAG 查阅代码库）、控制流（状态机、If-Else 规则拦截器）。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <h2 data-lake-id="\&quot;demo\&quot;" id="\&quot;demo\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uda1335d0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uda1335d0\&quot;">Demo</span></h2>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u786928b0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u786928b0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uae138419\&quot;" id="\&quot;uae138419\&quot;">理想实现：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucc89e501\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucc89e501\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0b2ab8ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0b2ab8ff\&quot;">bug 自动化流程，只针对 bug，比如产运或者研发发现当前项目存在 bug，可以通过飞书的方式提出，agent 将 bug 收集到列表进行统一管理，相当于一个待办清单，然后下游 agent 能够拉取未处理 bug，先对 bug 进行可行性分析，结合项目查看这个 bug 是否为真，如果是误报或者无法通过代码修复等情况就返回，如果可以修复就交给执行 agent 进行拉分支，写代码，写单测，相当于一个研发 agent，然后再交给测试 agent 进行二次处理，包括部署到测试环境联调等内容，联调通过后会给到运维 agent 进行上线，其中会有哨兵 agent 进行整个流程的管控，如果遇到某个 agent 出现错误或者流程终止需要对清单的任务状态进行处理变更和通知，相关于管理全局，其中也需要对整个流程进行监控。 </span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u56b1b4f4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u56b1b4f4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u17515b95\&quot;" id="\&quot;u17515b95\&quot;">该自动化流程应该可插拔，高扩展，强适配。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf88d097\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf88d097\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u63a97a57\&quot;" id="\&quot;u63a97a57\&quot;">demo思路：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u83573213\&quot;" id="\&quot;u83573213\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua55698ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua55698ff\&quot;">通过 ralph loop 让 claude code 循环执行未处理 bug，经手 bug 后处于 supervisor 状态，开启子 agent 并赋予相应 skill 分别执行分析、开发、测试动作，直到处理结束。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0fe0b242\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0fe0b242\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1776081545179-d7ed4810-5f01-4bd2-befd-3ed5329f7ecc.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue4f1d074-162d-4697-b5c0-fa357259180%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ueface7a3-e6cd-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1652%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1316%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22ALAUTOMATEDBUGFIXPIPELINEARCHITECTURE%22%2C%22x%22%3A591%2C%22y%22%3A16%2C%22width%22%3A638%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LAYER3%3ASKILLAGETS(EXECUTIONLAYER-L%22%2C%22x%22%3A263%2C%22y%22%3A1013%2C%22width%22%3A404%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LAYER0%3AFLASKVIEWER(HUMANLNTERFACE%22%2C%22x%22%3A546%2C%22y%22%3A94%2C%22width%22%3A372%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LAYER2%3ACLAUDECODE(ORCHESTRATIONBRAIN)%22%2C%22x%22%3A262%2C%22y%22%3A774%2C%22width%22%3A415%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LAYER1%3ARALPH(AUTO-LOOPENGINE%22%2C%22x%22%3A130%2C%22y%22%3A537%2C%22width%22%3A327%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22-LNTERNALMULTI-TURNLTERAT%22%2C%22x%22%3A639%2C%22y%22%3A1014%2C%22width%22%3A244%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22INGLESOURCEOFTRUTH%22%2C%22x%22%3A696%2C%22y%22%3A397%2C%22width%22%3A202%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CONFIRMED%2FREJECTE%22%2C%22x%22%3A329%2C%22y%22%3A1148%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22READ%2BWRITE(SUBMIT)%E4%B8%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A838%2C%22y%22%3A269%2C%22width%22%3A164%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TERATEUNTILPYTESTPASSES%22%2C%22x%22%3A661%2C%22y%22%3A1153%2C%22width%22%3A171%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STATE%2FBUGSJSON%22%2C%22x%22%3A739%2C%22y%22%3A376%2C%22width%22%3A161%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CODEREVIEW%2BEDGETEST%22%2C%22x%22%3A992%2C%22y%22%3A1131%2C%22width%22%3A172%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EDITCODE%2BWRITETESTS%22%2C%22x%22%3A665%2C%22y%22%3A1129%2C%22width%22%3A163%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22REVIEW%2BTESTAGEN%22%2C%22x%22%3A1009%2C%22y%22%3A1098%2C%22width%22%3A140%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22INDEPENDENTVERIFICATION%22%2C%22x%22%3A994%2C%22y%22%3A1153%2C%22width%22%3A172%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GREP%2BREADCODE%22%2C%22x%22%3A341%2C%22y%22%3A1129%2C%22width%22%3A160%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BASHWHILE-LOO%22%2C%22x%22%3A248%2C%22y%22%3A609%2C%22width%22%3A113%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STATEEILP%22%2C%22x%22%3A736%2C%22y%22%3A418%2C%22width%22%3A212%2C%22height%22%3A6%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BUGFLOW%22%2C%22x%22%3A422%2C%22y%22%3A19%2C%22width%22%3A131%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22FIXAPPLIED%22%2C%22x%22%3A668%2C%22y%22%3A1167%2C%22width%22%3A160%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PROMPTMD%22%2C%22x%22%3A1301%2C%22y%22%3A585%2C%22width%22%3A96%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22INSTMCTIONS%22%2C%22x%22%3A1303%2C%22y%22%3A617%2C%22width%22%3A93%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE--PRINT%22%2C%22x%22%3A247%2C%22y%22%3A629%2C%22width%22%3A113%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80CLAUDEPRINLB%2BPROMPTMD%22%2C%22x%22%3A387%2C%22y%22%3A701%2C%22width%22%3A266%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TRIAGEAGEN%22%2C%22x%22%3A360%2C%22y%22%3A1097%2C%22width%22%3A106%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22UG-TEST%22%2C%22x%22%3A1060%2C%22y%22%3A1062%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22READWRITE%22%2C%22x%22%3A987%2C%22y%22%3A360%2C%22width%22%3A95%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22FIXAGENT%22%2C%22x%22%3A700%2C%22y%22%3A1097%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RALPHRC%22%2C%22x%22%3A1120%2C%22y%22%3A600%2C%22width%22%3A66%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SETSTATUS%22%2C%22x%22%3A497%2C%22y%22%3A846%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22OOO%22%2C%22x%22%3A915%2C%22y%22%3A601%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SUBAGENT%22%2C%22x%22%3A708%2C%22y%22%3A843%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ROUTES%22%2C%22x%22%3A971%2C%22y%22%3A153%2C%22width%22%3A62%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TNEOUT%22%2C%22x%22%3A496%2C%22y%22%3A600%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22IRCULI%22%2C%22x%22%3A636%2C%22y%22%3A601%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PASS%2FFAIL%22%2C%22x%22%3A997%2C%22y%22%3A1169%2C%22width%22%3A159%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SGEAY%22%2C%22x%22%3A773%2C%22y%22%3A600%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LOCKBUG%22%2C%22x%22%3A494%2C%22y%22%3A829%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DISPATCH%22%2C%22x%22%3A710%2C%22y%22%3A823%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WRITEBACK%22%2C%22x%22%3A1115%2C%22y%22%3A828%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RESULT%22%2C%22x%22%3A931%2C%22y%22%3A845%2C%22width%22%3A48%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22READ%22%2C%22x%22%3A307%2C%22y%22%3A829%2C%22width%22%3A85%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22APP-PY%22%2C%22x%22%3A970%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BUG-ANA%22%2C%22x%22%3A353%2C%22y%22%3A1061%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RALPH%22%2C%22x%22%3A247%2C%22y%22%3A588%2C%22width%22%3A120%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BUGSJSON%22%2C%22x%22%3A310%2C%22y%22%3A847%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BUG-D%22%2C%22x%22%3A713%2C%22y%22%3A1064%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STATE%22%2C%22x%22%3A1122%2C%22y%22%3A847%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22100LINES%22%2C%22x%22%3A967%2C%22y%22%3A172%2C%22width%22%3A71%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PARSE%22%2C%22x%22%3A932%2C%22y%22%3A829%2C%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EAD%22%2C%22x%22%3A609%2C%22y%22%3A361%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SINGL%22%2C%22x%22%3A682%2C%22y%22%3A394%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BUGFORM%22%2C%22x%22%3A654%2C%22y%22%3A154%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A667%2C%22y%22%3A353%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80HEAA%2BWWRL%22%2C%22x%22%3A812%2C%22y%22%3A273%2C%22width%22%3A104%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23d6ecd7%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uac1b015d%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua50fbe34\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua50fbe34\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uce340665\&quot;" id="\&quot;uce340665\&quot;">问题点：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u69de3d71\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u611b84de\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u282c641c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u282c641c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaa3a22f0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaa3a22f0\&quot;">这种 subagent 模式是否能够应对一些中大型项目或者涉及多个文件修改的情况，如果更换为 multiagent 的实现方式又会不会实现的过于复杂，怎么保证可靠性，效果又如何？</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ol list="\&quot;u69de3d71\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;1\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ud3842fc2\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u0a0707ed\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0a0707ed\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua375362c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua375362c\&quot;">需要看看 cc 底层如何实现 subagent</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ol list="\&quot;u69de3d71\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u611b84de\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub7d740a6\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub7d740a6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u346a19d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u346a19d6\&quot;">流水线的核心更多强调一站式，处理前如何配置不同项目，接入飞书等应用提高便利和降低使用门槛，处理后该怎么接入测试环境并进行自动联调等操作。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ol list="\&quot;u69de3d71\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;1\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ub1df2aa6\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u179ffe2c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u179ffe2c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uffc62bdf\&quot;" id="\&quot;uffc62bdf\&quot;">当前有个思路，比如说某个项目出现 bug，可以提交描述和相应的项目，形成表格；后台会进行拉群操作，并实时播报处理进度，最后给出报告，包括处理结果，代码分支，测试环境部署地址等</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ol list="\&quot;u69de3d71\&quot;" start="\&quot;3\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u611b84de\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u652d3d72\&quot;" id="\&quot;u652d3d72\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uae697361\&quot;" id="\&quot;uae697361\&quot;">没有考虑到 agent 的自学习能力，如果这条链路其中一环出现问题，理应可以手动终止，并说明问题，agent 一旦确认，在执行成功后需要进行复盘，并执行记录，能够越用越聪明，实现方案参考 hermes agent，考量如何接入。</span></li>
  </ol>
