A252%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A49%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A%E9%9D%9EBUG%22%2C%22x%22%3A433%2C%22y%22%3A161%2C%22width%22%3A133%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22E2E%E8%81%94%E8%B0%83%22%2C%22x%22%3A1894%2C%22y%22%3A432%2C%22width%22%3A150%2C%22height%22%3A37%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%22%2C%22x%22%3A687%2C%22y%22%3A408%2C%22width%22%3A70%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%B9%BF%22%2C%22x%22%3A1141%2C%22y%22%3A673%2C%22width%22%3A186%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22-%E4%BA%8C---%E4%B8%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A1021%2C%22y%22%3A972%2C%22width%22%3A158%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%84%8F%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%9D%87%E5%8F%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A1131%2C%22y%22%3A870%2C%22width%22%3A148%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%BB%88%E6%80%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A2875%2C%22y%22%3A835%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcf4e7%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22udd1203b1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <h2 data-lake-id="\&quot;de958c1a\&quot;" id="\&quot;de958c1a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u910fddf0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u910fddf0\&quot;">PAUSED 机制</span></h2>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua4fa2dee\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua4fa2dee\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1c4d9a74\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1c4d9a74\&quot;">设计原则：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1166e4aa\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1166e4aa\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1eb4a4cd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1eb4a4cd\&quot;">任意状态都可能被人工打断——包括 DONE 和 REJECTED 等&quot;终态&quot;。人工无法实时盯着整个执行过程，流水线跑完后的事后审查同样可能发现问题。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf091f91b\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf091f91b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a8c4323\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a8c4323\&quot;">打断的本质都是同一件事：</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0f26ad68\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0f26ad68\&quot;">暂停流程、记录问题、等人工决策、恢复或改判</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub4f81278\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub4f81278\&quot;">。因此采用统一的 </span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;ua8962030\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua8962030\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u100dad2d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u100dad2d\&quot;">PAUSED</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8a0d411b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8a0d411b\&quot;"> 状态 + </span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;ube8f4a71\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube8f4a71\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf3bbb486\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf3bbb486\&quot;">paused_stage</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uac70d3c4\&quot;" id="\&quot;uac70d3c4\&quot;"> / </span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;u1feb203b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1feb203b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3ee0f76c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3ee0f76c\&quot;">error_origin_stage</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua807f50e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua807f50e\&quot;"> 字段，而非为每个阶段设置独立打断状态。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u41243379\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41243379\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2f9ced93\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2f9ced93\&quot;">PAUSED 的定位：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u57c6c261\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ub8d1529d\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub01676e3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub01676e3\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ube782424\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube782424\&quot;">暂停机制</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5ba57bc7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5ba57bc7\&quot;"> — 阻止 Agent 继续执行，等待人工决策</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ub8d1529d\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uedf0436c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uedf0436c\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u60f1a911\&quot;" id="\&quot;u60f1a911\&quot;">质量改进数据入口</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u41cf666a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41cf666a\&quot;"> — 每一次人工干预都沉淀为 intervention 记录，驱动 Skill 持续优化</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5cf24695\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5cf24695\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u990209e6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u990209e6\&quot;">自学习过程如下：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u383cadf6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u383cadf6\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
